<p itemprop="description">A trainee data scientist is inquisitive, curious about data and keen to learn and develop. They work under guidance and supervision to support data science activities.</p>

<section class="role-details">
    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Be aware of how data science techniques can be used, and have a basic knowledge of those key techniques, such as machine learning</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Support data exploration and analysis activities under supervision</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Learn and apply basic statistical and analytical techniques</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Contribute to team data science projects</li>
    </ul>
</section>

